Things have gotten better over time, but until now I haven't been able to bring myself to watch this mv or listen to the full Poet | Artist album. Watching the mv and finally starting to listen to the album has brought me both joy and sorrow. Joy because I can tell how much passion and hard work he put into creating this excellent album but sorrow because it's also a reminder that he's gone...
